<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.2/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.2/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
    <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="/css/styles.css">
    <title>Anne's Accessory Box</title>
</head>
<body>
    <%- include ('partials/navbar.ejs') %>
    <div class="container">
        <br>
        <h1>Welcome to Anne's Accessory Shop!</h1>
        <br>
        <div class="card-deck">
            <div class="card mb-3 mr-3">
                <div class="card-body">
                    <h5 class="card-title">Our Promise to you!</h5>
                    <p class="card-text">At Anne's Accessory Shop, we promise to all customers only the most beautiful and most secure accessories that you have ever seen!</p>
                    <p class="card-text">At this store, we only reserve the best for the best.</p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="card mb-3 mr-3">
                <div class="card-body">
                    <h5 class="card-title">A Wide Variety of Products!</h5>
                    <p class="card-text">At Anne's Accessory Shop, we only sell the finest (and cutest) types of beaded accessories and jewelery that you will ever see! Interested in what we have? Head over to the products page to find out more!</p>
                    <p class="card-text"><small class="text-muted">*All while stocks last!*</small></p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="card mb-3 mr-3">
                <div class="card-body">
                    <h5 class="card-title">Commissions</h5>
                    <p class="card-text">Commissions are open as of now! Feel free to send a commission form if customised beaded accessories are what you want to purchase from our shop!</p>
                    <p class="card-text"><small class="text-muted">*Terms and conditions may apply. Do feel free to contact us for any clarifications*</small></p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>